    dc:description "FIGURES 64–74. Sobarocephala protea Lonsdale & Marshall. 64, habitus, lateral view; 65, habitus, dorsal view; 66, head, frontal view; 67, head, lateral view; 68, wing; 69, sternite 5, ventral view; 70, terminalia, lateral view; 71, epandrium, cercus, surstylus, subepandrial sclerite, dorsal view; 72, hypandrium and phallus, ventral view; 73, hypandrium and phallus, lateral view; 74, apex of phallus, posterior view. Abbreviations: ej apod = ejaculatory apodeme; hypd = hypandrium; paraph = paraphallus; phapod = phallapodeme; st = sternite; subepand scl = subepandrial sclerite." ;
